<h1><hiragana>i</hiragana>-adjectives</h1>

<table class="example">
 <tr>
   <th> &nbsp; </th>
   <th> Informal </th>
   <th> Formal </th>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Present </td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>i</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>i desu</hiragana></span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Present Negative </td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>kunai</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>kunai desu</hiragana></span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Past</td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>katta</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>katta desu</hiragana></span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Past Negative</td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>kunakatta</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>kunakatta desu</hiragana><span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> <hiragana>te</hiragana>-form</td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>kute</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>kute</hiragana><span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Adverb</td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>ku</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>taka</hiragana><span><hiragana>ku</hiragana><span></td>
 </tr>
</table>

<h1><hiragana>na</hiragana>-adjectives</h1>

<table class="example">
 <tr>
   <th> &nbsp; </th>
   <th> Informal </th>
   <th> Formal </th>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Present </td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana> da</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana> desu</hiragana></span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Present Negative </td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana> dewa nai</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana> dewa arimasenn</hiragana></span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Past</td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana> datta</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana> deshita</hiragana></span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Past Negative</td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana>dewa nakatta</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana>dewa arimasenn deshita</hiragana><span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> <hiragana>te</hiragana>-form</td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana>de</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana>de</hiragana><span></td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td> Adverb</td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana>ni</hiragana></span></td>
   <td> <hiragana>benri</hiragana><span><hiragana>ni</hiragana><span></td>
 </tr>
</table>

<h1>Comparatives</h1>

<p>
In a comparison the other item is marked with <hiragana>yori</hiragana> and the adjective is left unchanged.
</p>

