<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr> <td> <hiragana>toukyou ha rondonn yori ooki desu. </hiragana> </td> </tr>
  <tr class="eigo"> <td> Tokyo is bigger than London. </td> </tr>
  <tr> <td> &nbsp; </td> </tr>
  <tr> <td> <hiragana>nihongo ha doitsugo yori kanntann desu. </hiragana> </td> </tr>
  <tr class="eigo"> <td> Japanese is simpler than German. </td> </tr>
</table>

